== 制作 ==

=== 概念 ===
{{Quote box
|width=35%
|quote=“我们从变革是如何包括创造更好的同理心的循环这一点开始：你属于你的家庭，你的家庭又属于你们的部落，接着两个部落连接起来，这时你就有了对河流这一侧的人的同理心，并对抗对岸的人……同理也可以推及村落、城市、州郡和国家……所以假设一个更字面意义上的同理心可以被星球上的八个个体触发……他们忽然从心理上感觉到了彼此，能够像在一个房间里一样直接交流。他们会如何反应？他们会做什么？……这意味着什么？世界会对这些异能人士作何反应？他们会接纳这一现状，还是击倒他们？这个假设给了我们一个装载着史无前例的行动，伟大构想和精湛特技的绝妙平台来制作一部剧集，并播放给这颗星球上的观众。”
|source=——[[约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基|约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基]]，联合创作人<ref name="cbr">{{cite web |url=http://www.cbr.com/jms-discusses-collaborating-with-wachowskis-for-netflixs-sense8/ |title=JMS Discusses Collaborating With Wachowskis For Netflix's 'Sense8' |author=Chris Arrant |date=2013-10-30 |work=Comic Book Resources|publisher=Valnet |accessdate=2016-08-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827000017/http://www.cbr.com/jms-discusses-collaborating-with-wachowskis-for-netflixs-sense8/ |archivedate=2016-08-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref>
|align=right
}}

据沃卓斯基姐妹所说，《超感8人组》来源于宣布剧集的数年之前的“一场关于科技如何同时连接和分离我们的深夜对话”。<ref name="PR">{{cite press release |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/only-on-netflix-sci-fi-giants-the-wachowskis-and-j-michael-straczynski-team-up-to-create-sense8-200215501.html |title=Only On Netflix: Sci-Fi Giants The Wachowskis And J. Michael Straczynski Team-Up To Create "Sense8" |date=2013-03-27 |location=Beverly Hills, California |publisher=[[Netflix|Netflix]] |agency=[[美通社|PR Newswire]]|accessdate=2014-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328090337/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/only-on-netflix-sci-fi-giants-the-wachowskis-and-j-michael-straczynski-team-up-to-create-sense8-200215501.html |archivedate=2016-03-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>斯特拉日恩斯基回忆，当沃卓斯基姐妹决定制作她们的首部剧集时，由于斯特拉日恩斯基在[[约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基#电视|这个领域的丰富经验]]，拉娜选择邀请他到自己位于旧金山的住所共同进行-{zh-hans:头脑风暴; zh-hant:腦力激盪}-。<ref name="cbr"/><ref name="collider">{{cite interview |url=http://collider.com/sense8-j-michael-straczynski-talks-collaborating-with-the-wachowskis/ |title=J. Michael Straczynski Talks Collaborating with The Wachowskis on SENSE8 |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |interviewer=Christina Radish |date=2015-05-26 |work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|publisher=Complex Media|accessdate=2015-05-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507145641/http://collider.com/sense8-j-michael-straczynski-talks-collaborating-with-the-wachowskis/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>他们三人都同意，如果他们要制作一部电视剧，他们想做一些“史无前例”的东西，<ref name="cbr2">{{cite interview |url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=52636 |title=J. Michael Straczynski Calls "Dream Police" Back into Action, Updates on "Sense8" |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |interviewer=Casey Gilly |date=2014-05-06 |work=Comic Book Resources|publisher=Valnet |accessdate=2014-10-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507141844/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=52636 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>并改变“电视制作的词汇表”，如同[[黑客帝国|黑客帝国]]曾做过的那样。<ref name="webpronews">{{cite web |url=http://www.webpronews.com/?p=262116 |title=Netflix's 'Sense8' Hopes To Do For TV What 'The Matrix' Did For Film |author=Chris Crum |date=2013-09-17 |work=WebProNews |accessdate=2015-09-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507142436/http://www.webpronews.com/?p=262116 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>讨论结束几天后他们决定他们会创作一部讨论人类竞争中介于[[同理心|同理心]]和[[演化|演化]]之间的人际关系，并以世界为尺度讲述故事，因此需要在全世界数个国家[[外景拍攝|外景拍攝]]，与试图尽可能限制或伪装外景的标准电视剧制作模式正好背道而驰。<ref name="cbr"/><ref name="awardsdaily"/>沃卓斯基灵感的来源之一是她自己想象的住在世界各地的朋友同时观看一部电影并在线上分享评论的体验。<ref name="collider"/>

拉娜在头脑风暴结束的第二天想出了剧集的名字，当时他们甚至还没有决定要有多少角色。<ref>{{cite interview |url=https://www.assignmentx.com/2015/j-michael-straczynski-on-sense8-exclusive-interview/ |title=SENSE8: J. Michael Straczynski talks Season 1- exclusive interview |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |interviewer=Abbie Bernstein |date=2015-08-17 |work=Assignment X |publisher=Midnight Productions |accessdate=2016-08-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826200508/https://www.assignmentx.com/2015/j-michael-straczynski-on-sense8-exclusive-interview/ |archivedate=2016-08-26 |deadurl=no}}</ref>拉娜带着一个写着“sense8”的笔记本去找斯特拉日恩斯基，这个词是“[[wiktionary:sensate|sensate]]”的谐音，并代表着8个主要角色，告诉他：“最困难的部分已经完成了！”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2015/06/05/sense8-netflix/ |title=8 Things to Help You Make Sense of 'Sense8' |author=John Jurgensen |date=2015-06-05 |work=[[华尔街日报|The Wall Street Journal]]|publisher=[[道琼斯公司|Dow Jones & Company]]|accessdate=2016-08-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826201110/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2015/06/05/sense8-netflix/ |archivedate=2016-08-26 |deadurl=no}}</ref>

=== 构思 ===
三人对他们想出的概念很是兴奋，他们决定自己围绕这个点子进行开发，而不是将它卖给他人。<ref name="cbr"/>沃卓斯基姐妹撰写了三小时长的[[待售劇本|待售劇本]]，<ref name="Variety2">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2012/tv/news/wachowskis-shopping-their-first-tv-series-1118060175/ |title=Wachowskis shopping their first TV series |date=2012-10-02 |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|accessdate=2014-10-19 |author=Cynthia Littleton |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507143112/http://variety.com/2012/tv/news/wachowskis-shopping-their-first-tv-series-1118060175/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>并同斯特拉日恩斯基一道像[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]和[[HBO|HBO]]之类的公司推销它。<ref name="collider2">{{cite interview |url=http://collider.com/wachowskis-jupiter-ascending-interview/ |title=The Wachowskis Talk JUPITER ASCENDING, Creating the Chicago Sequence, SENSE8, and More |subject=The Wachowskis |subjectlink=華卓斯基姐妹 |interviewer=Steve 'Frosty' Weintraub |date=2015-02-04 |work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|publisher=Complex Media|accessdate=2016-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031114300/http://collider.com/wachowskis-jupiter-ascending-interview/ |archivedate=2016-10-31 |deadurl=no}}</ref>但当他们发现没有人能理解这个概念，所以他们决定将剧本搁置。<ref name="awardsdaily">{{cite interview |url=http://www.awardsdaily.com/tv/interview-sense8-straczynski/ |title=Straczynski Talks 'Sense8' and the Outrageous Show's Diversity |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |interviewer=Jazz Tangcay |date=2016-06-09 |work=AwardsDaily TV |accessdate=2016-06-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610215350/http://www.awardsdaily.com/tv/interview-sense8-straczynski/ |archivedate=2016-06-10 |deadurl=no}}</ref>几年后，当他们觉得电视界的环境已变得对实验性的概念更友好的时候，他们决定开始新一轮的推销。<ref name="awardsdaily"/>2012年10月2日，《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》杂志第一个曝光了这个项目，并称在姐妹二人自己所有的Studio JMS和Georgeville Television的帮助下，她们会在接下来的一周里向洛杉矶各电视台推销《超感8人组》。<ref name="Variety2"/>如果剧集被选中立项，姐妹二人和斯特拉日恩斯基会轮流运营。此外，如果时间允许，沃卓斯基姐妹计划导演其中的几集。据斯特拉日恩斯基所说，他们见的第一个潜在买家就是Netflix。沃卓斯基姐妹和特斯拉日恩斯基与Netflix讨论了诸如[[性別_(文化)|性别]]、[[身份认同|身份认同]]、[[保密性|保密]]和[[隐私权|隐私权]]之类的主题。<ref name="indiewire">{{cite interview |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/sense8-co-creator-j-michael-straczynski-interview-netflix-season-2-20150605 |title='Sense8' Co-Creator J. Michael Straczynski on How Netflix's Show Changed Him, and Could Change Television |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |interviewer=Liz Shannon Miller |date=2015-06-06 |work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|accessdate=2015-06-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507143303/http://www.indiewire.com/article/sense8-co-creator-j-michael-straczynski-interview-netflix-season-2-20150605 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>而据拉娜所说，他们在全球取景的要求得到了Netflix的积极回应，与他们与其他几家播出平台已流产的接触中“没门”的回应截然相反。<ref name="collider2"/>他们亦告诉Netflix他们只接受能“做任何事”的条件，比如“有着各种肉体的心灵{{link-en|狂欢会|orgies}}”以及“甚至是{{link-en|活产 (人类)|Live birth (human)|活产}}镜头”，Netflix也欣然接受。<ref name="io9"/>会面过后，尽管一切似乎都很顺利，<ref name="cbr"/>他们却担心他们犯了错，因为他们没有敲定任何行动，也没有提及商业方面。<ref name="indiewire"/>中午之前，他们还没来得及接触HBO或其他播出平台，<ref name="webpronews"/> Netflix就致电抢先签下了第1季。<ref name="cbr"/>2013年3月27日，Netflix宣布订购10集长的第1季。<ref name="PR"/>之后，在拍摄期间，<ref>{{cite web |title=Andy und Lana Wachowski: Nerds mit zwölfstöckigen Gehirnen |url=http://www.faz.net/aktuell/feuilleton/medien/andy-und-lana-wachowski-nerds-mit-zwoelfstoeckigen-gehirnen-13412132.html?printPagedArticle=true |publisher=[[法兰克福汇报|Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung]]|work=FAZ.NET |accessdate=2015-02-14 |trans-title=Andy and Lana Wachowski: Nerds With twelve-story Brains| language=de |author=Nina Rehfeld |date=2015-02-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507145351/http://www.faz.net/aktuell/feuilleton/medien/andy-und-lana-wachowski-nerds-mit-zwoelfstoeckigen-gehirnen-13412132.html?printPagedArticle=true |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>基于剧本的高密度和被扩展的第1集第1场，制作人和Netflix达成协议，将第1季扩增至12集。<ref name="collider"/>

拍摄开始之前，斯特拉日恩斯基和沃卓斯基姐妹勾勒出了该剧共5季的蓝图，<ref name="collider"/>包括该剧的剧终集，就如同斯特拉日恩斯基曾在剧集《[[巴比伦5号|巴比伦5号]]》中做过的那样。<ref name="nerdist">{{cite interview |url=http://nerdist.com/exclusive-j-michael-straczynski-prepares-us-for-his-netflix-series-sense8/ |title=Exclusive: J. Michael Straczynski Prepares Us for His Netflix Series SENSE8 |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |interviewer=Joseph McCabe |date=2015-06-06 |work=Nerdist |accessdate=2015-06-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507150011/http://nerdist.com/exclusive-j-michael-straczynski-prepares-us-for-his-netflix-series-sense8/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>演员一次性签约5季。“我们敲定了一个长达五年的故事。我们已经勾勒出了5季的骨架，我们的演员合约按5季签署，最终有5季还是6季取决于间歇期”斯特拉日恩斯基说。<ref name="screener">{{cite interview |url=http://screenertv.com/blog-post/netflixs-sense8-details-and-a-new-comic-from-j-michael-straczynski/ |title=Netflix's 'Sense8' details and a new comic from J. Michael Straczynski |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |interviewer=Andrea Reiher |date=2014-02-03 |work=Screener|publisher=Tribune Media|accessdate=2016-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031120227/http://screenertv.com/blog-post/netflixs-sense8-details-and-a-new-comic-from-j-michael-straczynski/ |archivedate=2016-10-31 |deadurl=no}}</ref>第1季作为系列的{{link-en|起源故事|origin story}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nerdist.com/j-michael-straczynski-and-the-cast-of-netflixs-sense8-look-ahead-to-season-2/ |title=J. Michael Straczynski and the Cast of Netflix's SENSE8 Look Ahead to Season 2 |author=Joseph McCabe |date=2015-08-06 |work=Nerdist< |via=Nerdist |accessdate=2016-11-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107004112/http://nerdist.com/j-michael-straczynski-and-the-cast-of-netflixs-sense8-look-ahead-to-season-2/ |archivedate=2016-11-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>当被问及他们的[[權威書籍|宝典]]有多长的时候，斯特拉日恩斯基回答“它在我们的脑海里”。<ref name="indiewire"/>然而，斯特拉日恩斯基的确曾编纂过一份30页的文档，假设第1季获得成功，第2季的关键点会是什么。<ref name="hitfix">{{cite interview |url=http://www.hitfix.com/the-fien-print/j-michael-straczynski-says-viewers-have-evolved-to-be-ready-for-sense8 |title=J. Michael Straczynski says viewers have evolved to be ready for 'Sense8' |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |interviewer=Daniel Fienberg |date=2015-06-05 |work=[[HitFix|HitFix]] |accessdate=2015-06-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507150217/http://www.hitfix.com/the-fien-print/j-michael-straczynski-says-viewers-have-evolved-to-be-ready-for-sense8 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>

漫画书作家{{link-en|史蒂夫·斯格罗斯|Steve Skroce}}从《[[黑客帝国|黑客帝国]]》起就与沃卓斯基姐妹有了电影和漫画书两方面的合作，并为本剧画了[[分鏡|分鏡]]。<ref>{{cite interview |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/68084 |title=AICN COMICS Q&@: Bug chats with uber-talented artist Steve Skroce about the Wachowskis' DOC FRANKENSTEIN! |subject=Steve Skroce |interviewer=ambush bug |date=2014-07-22 |work=Ain't It Cool News|accessdate=2014-12-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507150700/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/68084 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>朱莉·沃卓斯基，两人的妹妹，在第1季{{link-en|片尾字幕|closing credits}}中作为“故事研究员”署名。<ref name="creditsS1">{{cite episode |title=Limbic Resonance |series=Sense8 |season=1 |number=1 |network=[[Netflix|Netflix]] |date=2015-06-05}}</ref>

