=== 撰写 ===
第1季的剧本初稿由三位创作人分担撰写：沃卓斯基姐妹撰写第1、2、3、7、8集剧本，而斯特拉日恩斯基撰写第4、5、6、9、10集。随后他们交换剧本进行润色。斯特拉日恩斯基称剧本中一个绝妙的部分是由他和拉娜撰写的。<ref>{{cite interview |url=http://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/13-questions-about-netflixs-new-series-sense8-answered/ |title=13 Questions About Netflix's New Series Sense8 Answered |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |interviewer=Sarah Ricard |date=2015-06-03 |work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2015-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507192707/http://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/13-questions-about-netflixs-new-series-sense8-answered/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>斯特拉日恩斯基相信这样的写作方式能够掩盖各自的短处，并有利于相互学习。<ref name="lightspeedmagazine">{{cite interview |url=http://www.lightspeedmagazine.com/nonfiction/interview-j-michael-straczynski/ |title=Interview: J. Michael Straczynski |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |work=Lightspeed|accessdate=2016-05-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507193017/http://www.lightspeedmagazine.com/nonfiction/interview-j-michael-straczynski/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="creativescreenwriting">{{cite interview |url=http://creativescreenwriting.com/sense8/ |title="Both collaborative and challenging." Straczynski on Sense8 |subject=J. Michael Straczynski |subjectlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |interviewer=Sam Roads |date=2016-07-07 |work=Creative Screenwriting |publisher=CS Publications |accessdate=2016-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915211217/http://creativescreenwriting.com/sense8/ |archivedate=2016-09-15 |deadurl=no}}</ref>他认为动作戏和情节是她们最大的优势，而叙事结构则有所不足。而另一方面，他觉得自己擅长结构而短于动作。<ref name="lightspeedmagazine"/>斯特拉日恩斯基说他工作的方式是先在头脑里想出完整的剧本，从头至尾，再将其写下来，而沃卓斯基姐妹会先写下她们已经想好的场景，把还没有想好的部分暂时丢下，她们不断地交换各个部分的位置以求获得最好的效果。<ref name="creativescreenwriting"/>

早期版本的故事以一位来自伊拉克的通感者，并且反派低语者有更多的戏份。但后来编剧决定改变形式，减少叙事部分，除了介绍八位通感者的首集开场部分。<ref name="lightspeedmagazine"/>这意味着旧金山的戏份必须围绕诺米展开，芝加哥的戏份必须围绕威尔展开，诸如此类。由于一开始角色被设定为不知道正在发生什么，他们不能像传统剧集一样剪进反派的镜头，观众们一开始带着与角色相同的疑问和困惑。<ref name="hitfix"/><ref name="lightspeedmagazine"/>随着角色们逐在随后的几集中逐步明白他们身上发生了什么，观众也同步了解。斯特拉日恩斯基注意到如果他们是为[[电视联播网#美国|传统电视网]]创作，这种方法将不可行。“本剧的首集完全不同于传统[[電視試播|试播集]]。你必须在试播集设定好世界观、解释清楚一切来吸引观众，”斯特拉日恩斯基说。相反， 冒险在{{link-en|狂欢式观看|binge-watching}}平台的代表Netflix上推进项目，给了剧集以一种与众不同的步伐——像连续12小时的电影一样——讲述故事的可能性。<ref name="nerdist"/>

拉娜·沃卓斯基，一名女变性人，在本剧中创造了她生涯中首个[[跨性別|跨性別]]角色：诺米·马克斯。她在这个角色身上部分融入了 自己的经历。“其中有部分紧绷的、[[自传|自传]]性质的场景，这有点困难，有点超现实，”拉娜说。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagomag.com/arts-culture/May-2015/Wachowski-Netflix-Series-Sense8/ |title=The Wachowski Netflix Series Sense8 Finally Has a Trailer |author=Emmet Sullivan |date=2015-05-07 |work=Chicago|accessdate=2015-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507193403/http://www.chicagomag.com/arts-culture/May-2015/Wachowski-Netflix-Series-Sense8/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>斯特拉日恩斯基声称就像拉娜对诺米有共鸣一样，他对沃夫冈·波格丹诺夫这个角色也颇有感触，因为他们都与各自的父亲关系很糟糕。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbr.com/j-michael-straczynski-is-cautiously-optimistic-about-a-second-season-of-sense8/ |title=J. Michael Straczynski is 'Cautiously Optimistic' About a Second Season of 'Sense8' |date=2015-08-03 |author=Scott Huver |work=Comic Book Resources|publisher=Valnet |accessdate=2016-08-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827000445/http://www.cbr.com/j-michael-straczynski-is-cautiously-optimistic-about-a-second-season-of-sense8/ |archivedate=2016-08-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref>“故事叙述中，沃夫冈是我的‘正北’，”斯特拉日恩斯基说。<ref name="indiewire"/>斯特拉日恩斯基没有透露在撰写过程中，莉莉·沃卓斯基对哪个角色感同身受，他说要由她自己决定是否要揭晓。<ref name="indiewire"/>此后莉莉也作为跨性别者出柜。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.windycitymediagroup.com/lgbt/Second-Wachowski-filmmaker-sibling-comes-out-as-trans-/54509.html |title=Second Wachowski filmmaker sibling comes out as trans |author=Tracy Baim |date=2016-03-08 |work=Windy City Times|accessdate=2016-05-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507194002/http://www.windycitymediagroup.com/lgbt/Second-Wachowski-filmmaker-sibling-comes-out-as-trans-/54509.html |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>她变性的过程开始于第1季发布之前，而诺米·马克斯的扮演者杰米·克莱顿对此事早已知晓。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lilly-wachowski-sharing-her-trans-880353 |title=Lilly Wachowski on Sharing Her Trans Journey: "You're Not Always Going to Change People's Minds" |author=Chris Gardner |date=2016-04-04 |work=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=2016-05-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507194159/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lilly-wachowski-sharing-her-trans-880353 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.etonline.com/news/186088_lilly_wachowski_on_following_sister_s_footsteps_through_her_transition/ |title=EXCLUSIVE: Lilly Wachowski on Following in Sister's Footsteps Through Her Transition |author=Stacy Lambe |date=2016-04-05 |work=Entertainment Tonight|accessdate=2016-05-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507194421/http://www.etonline.com/news/186088_lilly_wachowski_on_following_sister_s_footsteps_through_her_transition/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>

与第1季三人分头工作、频繁开会的方式不同的是，<ref name="cbr"/>第2季的撰写是在一个共同的编剧室中完成的。<ref name="lightspeedmagazine"/>

=== 选角 ===
对于美国之外的角色，制片人想要组建一个国际化的演员阵容，而且演员要尽可能有鲜明的国家特征。比如，瑞麦尔特、德赛和裴斗娜同他们分别的角色一样来自柏林、孟买和首尔。<ref name="hitfix"/>因为8个主要角色有着同一个生日，所选择的演员都在二十多岁至三十多岁之间。<ref name="screener"/>制片人想要一个中日韩角色，而又因为沃卓斯基在《云图》和《[[木星上行|木星上行]]》中与裴斗娜有过合作，他们决定为她创作一个韩国角色。<ref name="hitfix"/> 裴斗娜对合约中5季的计划很是忧虑，因为这意味着她接下来的十年都要拍动作戏，会对她结婚怀孕有影响。创作人告诉她不必忧虑，如果这些事真的发生了，他们可以让她的角色直接“领便当”，于是她加入了剧组。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2016/07/bae-doo-na-talks-about-how-long-shell-work-on-her-netflix-series-sense8 |title=Bae Doo Na talks about how long she'll work on her Netflix series 'Sense8' |author=beansss |date=2016-07-01 |work=[[Allkpop|Allkpop]]|publisher=6Theory Media |accessdate=2016-08-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821133546/http://www.allkpop.com/article/2016/07/bae-doo-na-talks-about-how-long-shell-work-on-her-netflix-series-sense8 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |deadurl=no}}</ref>米德尔顿在拍摄《木星上行》时已经知道沃卓斯基姐妹在写《超感8人组》的剧本，但她并不认为她们会请她出演。<ref name="irishnews">{{cite web |url=http://www.irishnews.com/arts/2015/06/19/news/rising-film-star-middleton-is-tupp-of-the-world-138543/ |title=Rising film star Middleton is Tupp of the world |work=The Irish News|date=2015-06-19 |accessdate=2016-05-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507194729/http://www.irishnews.com/arts/2015/06/19/news/rising-film-star-middleton-is-tupp-of-the-world-138543/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>克莱顿同她所扮演的角色一样是个跨性别者。她被《超感8人组》所吸引，因为这是个在一个跨性别导演兼编剧手下扮演一个跨性别者的机会，而且她还是科幻和斯特拉日恩斯基的粉丝。><ref name="Claytoncast">{{cite interview |url=http://collider.com/sense8-jamie-clayton-talks-wachowskis-her-character-and-more/ |title=SENSE8: Jamie Clayton Talks Working with The Wachowskis, Her Character, and More |subject=Jamie Clayton |interviewer=Christina Radish |date=2015-06-03 |work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|publisher=Complex Media|accessdate=2016-06-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611235727/http://collider.com/sense8-jamie-clayton-talks-wachowskis-her-character-and-more/ |archivedate=2016-06-11 |deadurl=no}}</ref>汉娜作为低语者的候选者被带到剧组，因为当时他们觉得可以让她扮演一个去性别化的角色， 但当她到来之后，他们告诉她他们想让她扮演安吉利卡。<ref>{{cite interview |url=http://collider.com/sense8-daryl-hannah-interview/ |title=SENSE8 Interview: Daryl Hannah Reflects on Performing in the Wachowskis' Latest Project |subject=Daryl Hannah |subjectlink=戴露·漢娜 |interviewer=Christina Radish |date=2015-06-10 |work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|publisher=Complex Media|accessdate=2016-05-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507194925/http://collider.com/sense8-daryl-hannah-interview/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>{{link-en|克里斯蒂安·奥利弗|Christian Oliver}}曾参与《[[極速賽車手|極速賽車手]]》，他对在沃卓斯基的作品中再次扮演反派很是兴奋。<ref>{{cite interview |url=http://www.myfanbase.de/serien/sense8/interviews/?pid=21491 |title=Exclusive interview with Christian Oliver |subject=Christian Oliver |interviewer=Nicole Oebel |date=2015-05-31 |work=myFanbase |accessdate=2016-11-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101234213/http://www.myfanbase.de/serien/sense8/interviews/?pid=21491 |archivedate=2016-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>{{link-en|乔·潘多利亚诺|Joe Pantoliano}}曾参与沃卓斯基姐妹的电影《[[驚世狂花|驚世狂花]]》和《黑客帝国》，此次扮演不署名角色威尔的父亲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/sense8/35693/sense8-season-1-review |title=Sense8 season 1 review |author=Jules-Pierre Malartre |date=2015-06-08 |work=Den Of Geek |publisher=Dennis Publishing|accessdate=2016-12-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230171642/http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/sense8/35693/sense8-season-1-review |archivedate=2016-12-30 |deadurl=no}}</ref>

2016年4月26日，《最后期限》杂志报道艾敏在第2季已经制作数集时突然退出，由于与沃卓斯基姐妹一场源于该季拍摄开始时一次不欢而散的{{link-en|席间谈话|table read}}的愈演愈烈的争执。}<ref name="recast">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/sense8-aml-ameen-toby-onwumere-recasting-wachowski-netflix-series-1201744886/ |title='Sense8': Aml Ameen Replaced By Toby Onwumere In Wachowskis' Netflix Series |date=2016-04-26 |publisher=Penske Media Corporation|author1=Nellie Andreeva |author2=Mike Fleming Jr |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2016-04-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507132635/http://deadline.com/2016/04/sense8-aml-ameen-toby-onwumere-recasting-wachowski-netflix-series-1201744886/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>《最后期限》文章及艾敏的搭档杜蓬斯·米德尔顿都指出这些争执只是“创意分歧”（[[wikt:en:creative_differences|creative differences]]）。<ref name="buzzfeed3"/>当被问及此事，斯特拉日恩斯基表示他不在场，不知道艾敏与拉娜之间发生了什么，但他尊重两人的选择。<ref>{{cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X6SYh5nK13A |title='Sense8' creator J. Michael Straczynski on sex, diversity & global perspective |author=Daniel Montgomery |date=2016-06-10 |via=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |publisher=Gold Derby|type=Webcam interview |time=14:02 |accessdate=2016-10-29}}</ref>随着艾敏的退出，坎普斯的角色由托比·盎乌迈尔在经过七天试镜后接手。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/sense8-cast-swoops-into-chicago-for-second-season-filming/ |title='Sense8' cast swoops into Chicago for second season filming |author=Talia Beechick |date=2016-07-07 |work=[[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]]|publisher=Sun-Times Media Group|accessdate=2016-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708020429/http://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/sense8-cast-swoops-into-chicago-for-second-season-filming/ |archivedate=2016-07-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>由于他从没有看过这部剧，盎乌迈尔专门为了试镜而观看了几集。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/12/sense8-capheus-recast-toby-onwumere-season-2-lana-wachowski-1201763899/ |title='Sense8': How Toby Onwumere, Season 2's New Capheus, Joined Lana Wachowski's Sensate Tribe |author=Liz Shannon Miller |date=2016-12-30 |work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|accessdate=2016-12-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231130837/http://www.indiewire.com/2016/12/sense8-capheus-recast-toby-onwumere-season-2-lana-wachowski-1201763899/ |archivedate=2016-12-31 |deadurl=no}}</ref>曾参与《极速赛车手》和《木星上行》的{{link-en|吉克·盖里|Kick Gurry}}接到拉娜的电话，通知他他们专门为他创作了一个角色。<ref name="forbes">{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/dongroves/2016/04/07/the-wachowskis-and-sense8-season-2-an-insiders-perspective/ |title=The Wachowskis And 'Sense8' Season 2: An Insider's Perspective |date=2016-04-07 |author=Don Groves |work=[[福布斯|Forbes]] |accessdate=2016-04-08 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824110940/http://www.forbes.com/sites/dongroves/2016/04/07/the-wachowskis-and-sense8-season-2-an-insiders-perspective/%2358dd3a7c65b0 |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>2016年9月，[[西爾維斯特·麥考伊|西爾維斯特·麥考伊]]透露他参与了某部Netflix剧集三至四集的录制，随后被证实其参与的正是《超感8人组》，并且如果他希望的话，可以签约更多季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mymbuzz.com/2016/09/24/doctor-whos-sylvester-mccoy-lands-role-in-netflix-series-sense8/ |title=Doctor Who's Sylvester McCoy Lands Role In Netflix Series Sense8 |author=Dave Golder |date=2016-09-24 |work=MyM BUZZ |accessdate=2016-09-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924231830/http://www.mymbuzz.com/2016/09/24/doctor-whos-sylvester-mccoy-lands-role-in-netflix-series-sense8/ |archivedate=2016-09-24 |deadurl=no}}</ref>曾出演《云图》中一个小角色的{{link-en|马丁·乌特克|Martin Wuttke}}亦加入了第2季剧组。<ref name="creditsXmas"/>

