=== 拍摄与取景 ===

为了适当地表现这个故事国际化的一面，《超感8人组》剧组几乎走遍了全球。 第1季在8个国家的9个城市摄制：[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]、[[旧金山|旧金山]]、[[伦敦|伦敦]]、[[柏林|柏林]]、[[首爾|首爾]]、[[雷克雅維克|雷克雅維克]]、[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]、[[奈洛比|奈洛比]]和[[孟买|孟买]]。<ref name="Deadline"/><ref name="io9">{{cite interview |url=http://io9.com/the-wachowskis-say-they-filmed-a-live-birth-for-their-t-1683307179 |title=The Wachowskis Say They Filmed A Live Birth For Their TV Show Sense8 |subject=The Wachowskis |subjectlink=沃卓斯基姐妹 |interviewer=Meredith Woerner |date=2015-02-02 |work=io9|publisher=Gawker Media|accessdate=2015-02-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508005049/http://io9.gizmodo.com/the-wachowskis-say-they-filmed-a-live-birth-for-their-t-1683307179 |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>制作首先于2014年6月18日在旧金山开始。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nbcbayarea.com/news/local/The-Wachowskis-Sense8-Netflix-Series-San-Francisco-263721841.html |title=The Wachowskis Begin Filming of New Netflix Series, Sense8, in San Francisco |author=Josh Keppel |date=2014-06-18 |work=NBC Bay Area|accessdate=2016-05-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518000805/http://www.nbcbayarea.com/news/local/The-Wachowskis-Sense8-Netflix-Series-San-Francisco-263721841.html |archivedate=2016-05-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>制片人与“{{link-en|号角胡同壁画项目|Clarion Alley Mural Project}}”的负责人协商成功，让艺术家们用作品点缀剧集。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://missionlocal.org/2014/06/clarion-alley-artists-cool-with-netflix/ |title=Clarion Alley Artists Cool with Netflix |author=Daniel Hirsch |date=2014-06-24 |work=Mission Local|accessdate=2014-10-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508005547/http://missionlocal.org/2014/06/clarion-alley-artists-cool-with-netflix/ |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>芝加哥的摄制开始于7月9日，8月8日杀青，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenmag.com/story/2014/aug/08/10868/ |title=Wachowskis Wrap Today |date=2014-08-08 |author=Mike McNamara |work=Screen Magazine |accessdate=2014-10-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508005948/http://screenmag.com/story/2014/aug/08/10868/ |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>摄制同时取实景及在Cinespace Film Studios的摄影indianexpress棚进行。<ref name=July7>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/celebrity/chi-sense-8-filming-in-chicago-netflix-wachowski-20140707-column.html |title=Netflix's 'Sense8' begins filming in Chicago this week |author=Luis Gomez |work=[[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] |publisher=tronc|date=2014-07-07 |accessdate=2014-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508005337/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/celebrity/chi-sense-8-filming-in-chicago-netflix-wachowski-20140707-column.html |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>在{{link-en|实地拍摄|location scouting}}期间，出品人在[[印第安那州|印第安那州]][[加里_(印第安纳州)|加里]]发现了市卫理公会教堂，于是他们修改了剧本中对教堂的描述以在这里取景。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://posttrib.suntimes.com/news/lake/28695375-418/sci-fi-series-to-be-filmed-in-gary.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021224827/http://posttrib.suntimes.com/news/lake/28695375-418/sci-fi-series-to-be-filmed-in-gary.html |archivedate=2014-10-21 |title=Sci-fi series to be filmed in Gary |author=Michael Gonzalez |date=2014-07-16 |work=Post-Tribune|publisher=tronc|accessdate=2014-10-21 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>他们亦在芝加哥的“{{link-en|超级热狗|Superdawg}}”汽车通过式餐厅拍摄，期间顾客们被要求不要盯着剧组看。拉娜和莉莉是此地常客。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20140808/norwood-park/netflix-show-sense8-takes-over-superdawg |title=Netflix Show 'Sense8' Takes Over SuperDawg |author=Heather Cherone |date=2014-08-08 |work=DNAinfo.com|publisher=New Media News |accessdate=2014-10-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508010713/https://www.dnainfo.com/chicago/20140808/norwood-park/netflix-show-sense8-takes-over-superdawg |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>在德国的拍摄亦有在柏林城外[[巴貝爾斯堡攝影棚|巴貝爾斯堡攝影棚]]进行。<ref name="lvz">{{cite web |url=http://www.lvz.de/Kultur/Medien/Die-neue-Netflix-Produktion-Sense8-ist-eine-Episodenserie-der-Matrix-Macher |title=Die neue Netflix-Produktion "Sense8" ist eine Episodenserie der "Matrix"-Macher |author=Nina May |date=2015-06-01 |work=Leipziger Volkszeitung|accessdate=2015-06-05 |language=de |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508011057/http://www.lvz.de/Kultur/Medien/Die-neue-Netflix-Produktion-Sense8-ist-eine-Episodenserie-der-Matrix-Macher |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>在内罗毕的一场戏动用了700名[[臨時演員|臨時演員]]、200辆车和1架直升机。<ref name="mediamaxnetwork">{{cite web |url=http://mediamaxnetwork.co.ke/peopledaily/?p=105642 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008111925/http://mediamaxnetwork.co.ke/peopledaily/105642/hollywood-glitterati-brings-action-city/ |archivedate=2014-10-08 |title=Hollywood glitterati brings action to the city |date=2014-09-14 |work=People Daily |accessdate=2014-10-08 |deadurl=yes}} Also available at: [http://epaper.peopledaily.co.ke/?iid=101799&startpage=page0000002#folio=2 epaper.peopledaily.co.ke]</ref>在孟买，他们拍摄了一支由《[[貧民百萬富翁|貧民百萬富翁]]》的{{link-en|隆吉纳斯·费尔南德斯|Longinus Fernandes}}编排的[[宝莱坞|宝莱坞]]歌舞。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/english/hollywood/news/Choreographer-Longinus-Fernandes-set-to-work-with-Matrix-crew/articleshow/45166741.cms |title=Choreographer Longinus Fernandes set to work with Matrix crew |author=Piyali Dasgupta |date=2014-11-17 |work=[[印度时报|The Times of India]] |accessdate=2014-11-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508011730/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/english/hollywood/news/Choreographer-Longinus-Fernandes-set-to-work-with-Matrix-crew/articleshow/45166741.cms |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>编剧希望能在每个城市拍一场有当地特色的戏。<ref name="apdg">{{cite interview |url=http://www.apdg.org.au/interview-hugh-bateup-a-p-d-g-production-designer-sense8/ |title=INTERVIEW – HUGH BATEUP a.p.d.g – Production Designer – SENSE8 |subject=Hugh Bateup |date=2015-07-28 |work=Australian Production Design Guild |accessdate=2015-09-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508012138/http://www.apdg.org.au/interview-hugh-bateup-a-p-d-g-production-designer-sense8/ |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>他们成功地安排了在[[舊金山同志驕傲大遊行|舊金山同志驕傲大遊行]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.missionmission.org/2014/06/29/wachowskis-sense8-shooting-at-pride/ |title=Wachowski's Sense8 shooting at Pride |date=2014-06-29 |author=Ariel Dovas |work=Mission Mission |accessdate=2014-10-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508012433/http://www.missionmission.org/2014/06/29/wachowskis-sense8-shooting-at-pride/ |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>的{{link-en|女同性恋三月|Dyke March#San Francisco}}自行车上的活动、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.demotix.com/news/5129692/wachowskis-shoot-scenes-sense8-dyke-march-san-francisco |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706224510/http://www.demotix.com/news/5129692/wachowskis-shoot-scenes-sense8-dyke-march-san-francisco |title=The Wachowskis shoot scenes for Sense8 at Dyke March in San Francisco |date=2014-06-28 |author=Steve Rhodes |archivedate=2015-07-06 |work=Demotix|accessdate=2016-03-01 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>芝加哥[[美国独立日|美国独-{}-立日]]烟花秀和印度教节日{{link-en|象神节|Ganesha Chaturthi}}期间的拍摄。<ref name="s8docu">{{cite web |url=https://www.netflix.com/title/80062064 |title=Sense8: Creating the World |work=[[Netflix|Netflix]] |accessdate=2015-08-09 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150824023714/https://www.netflix.com/gb/title/80062064 |archivedate=2015-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>此外他们拍摄了一段旧金山鲜肉节期间的[[酷兒|酷兒]]表演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://archives.sfexaminer.com/sanfrancisco/fresh-meat-festival-promotes-transgender-artists/Content?oid=2823381 |title=Fresh Meat Festival promotes transgender artists |work=The San Francisco Examiner|date=2014-06-17 |author=Chloe Johnson |accessdate=2014-10-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508013536/http://archives.sfexaminer.com/sanfrancisco/fresh-meat-festival-promotes-transgender-artists/Content?oid=2823381%2F |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，伦敦{{tsl|en|KOKO (music venue)||KOKO}}的一次俱乐部活动，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwmusic/article/Wachowski-Siblings-UNKLE-Derrick-May-More-to-Participate-in-Generate-App-Launch-20140812 |title=Wachowski Siblings, UNKLE, Derrick May & More to Participate in 'Generate' App Launch |date=2014-08-12 |work=broadwayworld.com |accessdate=2014-10-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508014237/http://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwmusic/article/Wachowski-Siblings-UNKLE-Derrick-May-More-to-Participate-in-Generate-App-Launch-20140812 |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>和在墨西哥城[[瑙卡尔潘|瑙卡尔潘]]体育馆一场真正的职业[[墨西哥摔角|墨西哥摔角]]，角斗士们还带着{{link-en|摔跤面具|Wrestling mask#The mask in Lucha Libre}}。<ref name="s8docu"/>最后，飞机上的戏份是剧组在伦敦飞往冰岛的航班上实景拍摄的。<ref name="apdg"/>2014年11月17日，斯特拉日恩斯基发推称主单元的拍摄已经完成，只有部分冰岛冬季的镜头要在下个月拍摄。<ref>{{Cite tweet |user=straczynski |number=534459302728048641 |title=Main unit shooting Sense8 has just wrapped! Absent some winter shots in Iceland next month Netflix season one principal photography is done! |date=2014-11-17 |author=J. Michael Straczynski |authorlink=約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基 |accessdate=2014-11-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508205308/https://twitter.com/straczynski/status/534459302728048641 |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>这些拍摄随后由于冰岛雪量不足延后至次年1月中旬，<ref name="apdg"/>全剧的[[杀青|杀青]]镜头于1月21日在雷克雅未克的{{link-en|哈帕音乐厅|Harpa (concert hall)}}拍摄完成。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://icelandmag.com/article/sense8-throws-a-wrap-party-harpa-music-hall |title=Sense8 throws a wrap party at Harpa music Hall |date=2015-01-22 |work=Iceland Magazine |accessdate=2015-02-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508201326/http://icelandmag.visir.is/article/sense8-throws-a-wrap-party-harpa-music-hall |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>在摄制结束时，制作者们已经积累了{{convert|100000|mile|km|-3}}，相当于绕地球四圈。<ref name="io9"/>

第2季主单元的制作原定2016年3月开始，<ref name="thefilmstage">{{cite interview |url=http://thefilmstage.com/features/john-toll-talks-adjusting-for-the-small-screen-sense8-the-wachowskis-more/ |title=John Toll Talks Adjusting for the Small Screen, 'Sense8,' the Wachowskis & More |subject=John Toll |interviewer=Nick Newman |date=2015-11-24 |work=The Film Stage |accessdate=2015-11-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509123101/https://thefilmstage.com/features/john-toll-talks-adjusting-for-the-small-screen-sense8-the-wachowskis-more/ |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>但一场有主要演员参与的镜头2015年12月30日{{link-en|圣诞季|Christmas and holiday season}}期间在柏林开拍。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/1107089/sense8-rajans-the-new-big-bad-and-other-theories-about-season-2 |title=Sense8: Rajan's the new 'big bad' and 7 other theories about Season 2 |date=2015-12-23 |author=Carrie Nelson |work=SheKnows|accessdate=2015-12-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509123512/http://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/1107089/sense8-rajans-the-new-big-bad-and-other-theories-about-season-2 |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>接着他们又于2016年1月23日至24日在芝加哥进行了短暂的拍摄。<ref name="reelchicago">{{cite web |url=http://reelchicago.com/article/three-new-shows-set-cinespace-ready-roll160121 |title=Three new shows set up at Cinespace ready to roll |author=Ruth L Ratny |date=2016-01-21 |work=ReelChicago |accessdate=2016-01-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509123904/http://reelchicago.com/article/three-new-shows-set-cinespace-ready-roll160121 |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>2016年3月中旬拍摄在柏林继续，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.morgenpost.de/berlin/article207183749/In-Wilmersdorf-schneits-fuer-Netflix.html |title=In Wilmersdorf schneit's für Netflix |author=Martin Nejezchleba |date=2016-03-13 |work=Berliner Morgenpost|accessdate=2016-03-13 |language=de |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509124124/http://www.morgenpost.de/berlin/article207183749/In-Wilmersdorf-schneits-fuer-Netflix.html |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>接着25日开始在孟买继续进行了10天的拍摄。<ref name="indianexpress">{{cite web |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/anupam-kher-starts-shooting-for-sense8-season-two/ |title=Anupam Kher starts shooting for 'Sense8' season two |date=2016-03-26 |work=[[印度快報|The Indian Express]] |accessdate=2016-03-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509124314/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/anupam-kher-starts-shooting-for-sense8-season-two/ |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>艾缪·艾敏在孟买的拍摄后离开剧组。<ref name="recast"/>4月7日在[[波西塔諾|波西塔諾]]的拍摄开始。<ref name="forbes"/>4月稍晚时候，盎乌迈尔顶替艾敏，拍摄移至墨西哥，<ref name="buzzfeed3"/>并在墨西哥城北小镇{{link-en|麦特佩克|Metepec}}进行了一日拍摄。<ref name="scifinow">{{cite web |url=http://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/sense8-recasts-aml-ameens-capheus-after-creative-differences/ |title=Sense8 recasts Aml Ameen's Capheus after "creative differences" |author=Poppy-Jay Palmer |date=2016-04-27 |work=SciFiNow|accessdate=2016-04-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509125305/http://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/sense8-recasts-aml-ameens-capheus-after-creative-differences/ |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>5月7日在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]旧金山的拍摄开始，拍摄持续至23日。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://filmsf.org/sites/default/files/Meetings/2016/Minutes%203.28.16%20DRAFT.pdf |title=MINUTES OF THE DATE MEETING – MARCH 28, 2016 |work=filmsf.org |format=pdf |accessdate=2016-05-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509135528/http://filmsf.org/sites/default/files/Meetings/2016/Minutes%203.28.16%20DRAFT.pdf |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>{{link-en|外景制片人|Location manager}}马修·瑞塔接到了公园与游憩部门的罚单，原因是在比利哥特山的一场浪漫戏期间“有人突然裸体”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sfchronicle.com/bayarea/article/Supes-and-Senate-candidates-pledge-to-uh-8348462.php |title=Supervisors seeking state Senate pledge to annoy each other |author=Lizzie Johnson |date=2016-07-08 |work=[[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] |publisher=[[赫斯特国际集团|Hearst]] |accessdate=2016-07-09 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824112728/http://www.sfchronicle.com/bayarea/article/Supes-and-Senate-candidates-pledge-to-uh-8348462.php |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>紧接着是一场在[[马利布_(加利福尼亚州)|马利布]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的短暂拍摄。<ref name="LA">{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BIa40e9hMCY/ |title=Suns out, guns out. The #Road2Sense8 hits Los Angeles. |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |date=2016-07-28 |accessdate=2016-12-06 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161206133740/https://www.instagram.com/p/BIa40e9hMCY/ |archivedate=2016-12-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite tweet |user=MPC_UK |author=Motion Picture Capital |number=735215269841231874 |title=Check out ponchohd's photo- #Sense8 now filming in Malibu |date=2016-05-24 |accessdate=2016-05-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526214517/https://twitter.com/MPC_UK/status/735215269841231874 |archivedate=2016-05-26 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BF1li_0oIB3/ |title=🎥Sense8 ⚡️ @netflix What is Lito doing with @themarcjacobs and @chardefrancesco !? 😁 Que hace Lito con @themarcjacobs y @chardefrancesco ? #loveLana #lanawachowski |author=Miguel Ángel Silvestre |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |date=2016-05-25 |accessdate=2016-05-26 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824115858/https://www.instagram.com/p/BF1li_0oIB3/ |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>在巴西[[聖保羅_(巴西)|圣保罗]]的拍摄包括了3月的第20届[[聖保羅同志大遊行|聖保羅同志大遊行]]的镜头。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://spcine.wordpress.com/2016/04/01/serie-sense8-tera-filmagens-na-parada-lgbt-de-sao-paulo/ |title=Série Sense8 terá filmagens na parada LGBT de São Paulo |work=Spcine |date=2016-04-01 |accessdate=2016-04-02 |language=pt |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509130718/https://spcine.wordpress.com/2016/04/01/serie-sense8-tera-filmagens-na-parada-lgbt-de-sao-paulo/ |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>芝加哥的拍摄始于6月5日，15日杀青，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/tv/ct-sense8-star-co-creator-lilly-wachowski-taking-time-off-from-show-20160526-story.html |title='Sense8' star: Co-creator Lilly Wachowski taking time off from show |author=Tracy Swartz |work=[[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]]|publisher=tronc|date=2016-05-26 |accessdate=2016-06-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605142347/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/tv/ct-sense8-star-co-creator-lilly-wachowski-taking-time-off-from-show-20160526-story.html |archivedate=2016-06-05 |deadurl=no}}</ref>紧接着是英国伦敦、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/sydney-confidential/kick-gurry-says-working-with-wachowski-sisters-as-good-as-it-gets/news-story/446215e0b051be3cf9a7d09e88601f03/ |title=Kick Gurry says working with Wachowski sisters as good as it gets |author=Jonathon Moran |date=2016-06-28 |subscription=yes |work=[[每日电讯报_(澳洲)|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=News Corp Australia|accessdate=2016-06-28}}</ref>[[劍橋|劍橋]]和[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]，<ref>{{Cite tweet |user=MPC_UK |author=Motion Picture Capital |number=745299811528740865 |title=Couple of new #Sense8Season2 locations 4 new cast member @gravygold! #Cambridge & #Scotland join the #Sense8 party! |date=2016-06-21 |accessdate=2016-06-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628123734/https://twitter.com/MPC_UK/status/745299811528740865 |archivedate=2016-06-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>7月4日杀青。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BHcIi9QDBts/ |title=July 4th: Buckingham Palace. London... I get up!!! That's a wrap in the UK for @sense8 ... This city man... What a loyal friend... Has gifted me some of the greatest times I could ever have imagined... Thank you London... Flying to another great city now to continue this wild adventure... #kixit #sense8 #vanhalen #jump #steelsprings |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |date=2016-07-04 |author=Kick Gurry |accessdate=2016-07-08 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824115656/https://www.instagram.com/p/BHcIi9QDBts/ |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>然后拍摄转移至[[荷兰|荷兰]][[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]和[[海牙|海牙]]，直至19日。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amsterdam.nl/gemeente/organisatie/ruimte-economie/economie/amsterdams/nieuwsbrieven/artikelen/februari-2016/amsterdam-filmstad/ |title=Amsterdam filmstad gaat door met filmcommissioner |work=Amsterdam.nl |date=2016-02-27 |accessdate=2016-03-23 |language=nl |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509130943/https://www.amsterdam.nl/gemeente/organisatie/ruimte-economie/economie/amsterdams/nieuwsbrieven/artikelen/februari-2016/amsterdam-filmstad/ |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>接下来是肯尼亚内罗毕<ref>{{Cite tweet |user=MPC_UK |author=Motion Picture Capital |number=756585461339058176 |title=More from @ma_silvestre from the #Sense8 #Nairobi shoot, feat. @toby_onwumere & #DoonaBae! |date=2016-07-22 |accessdate=2016-07-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160725191959/https://twitter.com/MPC_UK/status/756585461339058176 |archivedate=2016-07-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>和[[大韩民国|韩国]][[富川市|富川市]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3020676 |title=Netflix founder defends age checks, pixelation |author=Seo Ji-Eun |date=2016-07-01 |work=[[中央日報_(韓國)|JoongAng Ilbo]]|publisher=Song Philho |accessdate=2016-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160713001457/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3020676 |archivedate=2016-07-13 |deadurl=no}}</ref>后来，拍摄短暂地回到伦敦及柏林，直至9月中旬。<ref name="pronto">{{cite web |url=http://www.pronto.es/actualidad/miguel-angel-silvestre-entre-paula-y-yo-va-a-haber-300574102.html |title=Miguel Ángel Silvestre: "Entre Paula y yo va a haber escenas muy fuertes" |date=2016-07-04 |work=Pronto|accessdate=2016-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160713001614/http://www.pronto.es/actualidad/miguel-angel-silvestre-entre-paula-y-yo-va-a-haber-300574102.html |archivedate=2016-07-13 |deadurl=no |language=es}}</ref>最后他们在[[马耳他|马耳他]]{{link-en|卡坎拉|Kalkara}}摄影棚的水箱中进行了两天的拍摄。<ref name="pronto"/>2016年9月19日，随着在马耳他的摄制的完成，该季的所有拍摄正式杀青。<ref name="wrapS2MPC">{{Cite tweet |user=MPC_UK |author=Motion Picture Capital |number=777934880357421057 |title=Congratulations to cast & crew for wrapping up the incredible achievement / feat of endurance that is filming #Sense8Season2! |date=2016-09-19 |accessdate=2016-09-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919232653/https://twitter.com/MPC_UK/status/777934880357421057 |archivedate=2016-09-19 |deadurl=no}}</ref>

