剧集的导演按拍摄地点而不是按集指派，<ref>{{Cite tweet |user=straczynski |number=608139836961099776 |title=@sense8linked Bear in mind eps weren't assigned to directors, cities were, so Tom's stuff in Nairobi/Berlin is in all of the eps. |author=J. Michael Straczynski |authorlink=约瑟夫·迈克尔·斯特拉日恩斯基 |date=2015-06-08 |accessdate=2015-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508205713/https://twitter.com/straczynski/status/608139836961099776 |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>所以实际上并没有任何一集只有一名导演。<ref name="comingsoon">{{cite interview |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/features/444671-interview-director-james-mcteigue-on-survivor-and-netflixs-sense8 |title=Interview: Director James McTeigue on Survivor and Netflix's Sense8 |subject=James McTeigue |work=ComingSoon.net|publisher=CraveOnline|interviewer=Edward Douglas |date=2015-05-29 |accessdate=2015-05-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508201643/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/features/444671-interview-director-james-mcteigue-on-survivor-and-netflixs-sense8 |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>第1季拍摄期间，沃卓斯基负责在芝加哥和旧金山拍摄的场景，<ref name="July7"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://missionlocal.org/2014/06/wachowskis-filming-in-clarion-alley-for-new-series/ |title=Netflix Filming in Clarion Alley for New Series |author=Joe Rivano Barros |date=2014-06-20 |work=Mission Local|accessdate=2014-10-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508201848/http://missionlocal.org/2014/06/wachowskis-filming-in-clarion-alley-for-new-series/ |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>以及伦敦和冰岛这两个原定由斯特拉日恩斯基掌舵拍摄之地的工作。<ref name="cbr2"/>斯特拉日恩斯基最终因为这两处取景地有大量动作戏而将其让给沃卓斯基姐妹，<ref>{{cite podcast |url=http://www.stitcher.com/podcast/rotten-tomatoes-podcast/e/ep-129-j-michael-straczynski-talks-sense8-and-the-53-hour-39347328 |title=Ep. 129 - J. Michael Straczynski Talks Sense8 and the 53 Hour Screenplay |time=13:42 |via=Stitcher Radio |publisher=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-05-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508204401/http://www.stitcher.com/podcast/rotten-tomatoes-podcast/e/ep-129-j-michael-straczynski-talks-sense8-and-the-53-hour-39347328 |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>转而在[[後期製作|後期製作]]投入心力。<ref name="collider"/> [[詹姆斯·麦克特格|詹姆斯·麦克特格]]（《[[V字仇杀队|V字仇杀队]]》、《[[忍者刺客|忍者刺客]]》）负责在墨西哥、孟买及部分雷克雅未克的拍摄，<ref name="apdg"/>德国导演汤姆·提克威尔（《云图》）的作品《{{link-en|内罗毕半条命|Nairobi Half Life}}》给了沃卓斯基姐妹很深的印象，掌舵在柏林<ref name="tykwer1">{{cite web |url=http://fortsetzung.tv/2014/10/12/cologne-conference-von-britischen-thrillern-und-deutschen-grosprojekten/ |title=Cologne Conference: Von britischen Thrillern und deutschen Großprojekten |work=Fortsetzung.tv |author=Marcus Kirzynowski |date=2014-10-12 |accessdate=2016-08-23 |language=de |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823202749/http://fortsetzung.tv/2014/10/12/cologne-conference-von-britischen-thrillern-und-deutschen-grosprojekten/ |archivedate=2016-08-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref>和内罗毕的拍摄。<ref name="mediamaxnetwork"/>丹·格拉斯从《[[黑客帝国2：重装上阵|黑客帝国2：重装上阵]]》开始就是沃卓斯基姐妹的御用{{link-en|视觉效果总监|visual effects supervisor}}，在《超感8人组》继续担任此职，并执导首尔部分。<ref name="cinefex">{{cite interview |url=http://cinefex.com/blog/sense8/ |title=The Visual Effects of "Sense8" |subject=Dan Glass |interviewer=Graham Edwards |date=2015-06-16 |work=Cinefex|accessdate=2015-06-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508203730/http://cinefex.com/blog/sense8/ |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>尽管有时候不同单元的拍摄时同时进行的，沃卓斯基姐妹会到各个国家去与当地的负责导演合作。<ref name="thefilmstage"/>据报道，沃卓斯基姐妹执导了本是其他导演负责的西尔维斯特在墨西哥城的[[特技|特技]]动作场景、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latercera.com/noticia/entretencion/2015/05/661-631967-9-detras-de-las-camaras-de-sense8-la-primera-serie-de-los-hermanos-wachowski.shtml |title=Detrás de las cámaras de Sense8, la primera serie de los hermanos Wachowski |author=Matías de la Maza |date=2015-05-30 |work=Latercera |accessdate=2015-09-28 |language=es |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508204057/http://www.latercera.com/noticia/entretencion/2015/05/661-631967-9-detras-de-las-camaras-de-sense8-la-primera-serie-de-los-hermanos-wachowski.shtml |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>内罗毕的“云顿”巴士{{link-en|追车|Car chase#In film}}场景<ref name="mediamaxnetwork"/>和出现了[[開山刀|開山刀]]{{link-en|电影中的打斗|Combat in film|打斗戏}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://instagram.com/p/3zUOg7QEDP/ |title=Always give yourself a fighting chance, which is easier for Doona Bae than for most others. #Sense8 #BTS |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |date=2015-06-11 |accessdate=2015-06-24 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824114411/https://www.instagram.com/p/3zUOg7QEDP/ |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>沃卓斯基姐妹总共署名导演7集，麦克特格和提克威尔各2集，格拉斯1集。<ref name="gamesradar"/>《超感8人组》拍摄期间沃卓斯基姐妹每天完成10至15页剧本，远远超过她们在常规大制作电影中的每天2-3页。她们觉得这种方式给了她们很多压力，但同时莉莉觉得自己能适应这种节奏很让她激动。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hitfix.com/motion-captured/our-wachowskis-interview-continues-on-blockbuster-culture-and-911 |title=Our Wachowskis interview continues on blockbuster culture and 9/11 |author=Drew McWeeny |date=2015-02-05 |work=[[HitFix|HitFix]] |accessdate=2016-11-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101001226/http://www.hitfix.com/motion-captured/our-wachowskis-interview-continues-on-blockbuster-culture-and-911 |archivedate=2016-11-01 |deadurl=no}}</ref>提克威尔说他必须按照每天完成7分钟镜头的步伐拍摄，他也觉得这和电影的拍摄非常不同。<ref name="tykwer1"/>

在第2季，拉娜接手了剧集的很多方面，<ref name="awardsdaily"/>再加上她妹妹的休息，她作为导演的责任也加重了。<ref name="buzzfeed3"/>{{link-en|音效制作混音师|Production sound mixer}}史蒂夫·海伍德叙述说拉娜的导演风格是以双机位为标配，并用大概15至20分钟的“超[[长镜头|长镜头]]”开始拍摄。此外，拉娜的剧组没有任何[[排練|排練]]。“我们在镜头前排练得很有效果，”，海伍德说。如果剧本出现任何技术问题，拉娜希望演员能够即兴发挥继续拍摄，而不是喊 {{tsl|en|Cut (transition)#Verbal command||“cut”}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.audiomediainternational.com/recording/sense8-sound-recordists-discuss-working-with-the-wachowskis/06170 |title='Sense8' sound recordists discuss working with The Wachowskis |author=Adam Savage |date=2017-01-09 |work=Audio Media International |publisher=NewBay Media|accessdate=2017-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110213446/http://www.audiomediainternational.com/recording/sense8-sound-recordists-discuss-working-with-the-wachowskis/06170 |archivedate=2017-01-10 |deadurl=no}}</ref>麦克特格作为墨西哥单元导演回归。<ref name="MexicoS2">{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BGeyksoQEIQ/ |title=Welcome to Mexico City. The #Road2Sense8 continues. |date=2016-06-10 |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2016-12-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161231220621/https://www.instagram.com/p/BGeyksoQEIQ/ |archivedate=2016-12-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref>提克威尔作为内罗毕单元导演回归，但不再负责柏林部分，因为他正忙于自己的剧集《[[巴比伦柏林|巴比伦柏林]]》，<ref>{{cite interview |url=http://frontrowfeatures.com/features/exclusive-filmmaker-tom-tykwer-awaits-hologram-king-release-15455.html |title=EXCLUSIVE: Filmmaker Tom Tykwer Awaits 'A Hologram for the King' Release |subject=Tom Tykwer |interviewer=Angela Dawson |date=2016-04-22 |work=Front Row Features Wire |accessdate=2016-10-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029143252/http://frontrowfeatures.com/features/exclusive-filmmaker-tom-tykwer-awaits-hologram-king-release-15455.html |archivedate=2016-10-29 |deadurl=no}}</ref>与第1季相同的是，第2季的每一集只会有一位导演署名，本季都是拉娜。
<ref name="S2DirLana">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/12/sense8-christmas-special-trailer-season-2-netflix-lana-wachowski-1201759333/ |title='Sense8: A Christmas Special' Trailer: Hallelujah, Netflix's Trippiest Thriller Is Back for Season 2 |author=Liz Shannon Miller |date=2016-12-16 |work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|accessdate=2016-12-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216151802/http://www.indiewire.com/2016/12/sense8-christmas-special-trailer-season-2-netflix-lana-wachowski-1201759333/ |archivedate=2016-12-16 |deadurl=no}}</ref>

=== 拍攝 ===
Netflix要求本剧用4K摄像机拍摄，以保证其不易过时，以主要{{link-en|摄像导演|director of photography}}身份署名的{{link-en|约翰·托尔|John Toll}}查看了9个各具特色的拍摄地点不同的外观特点，并决定使用索尼{{tsl|en|CineAlta|}} PMW-F55摄像机<ref name="thefilmstage"/>搭配[[蔡司公司|卡尔·蔡司Ultra Prime]]<ref name="F55S2">{{cite magazine |url=https://issuu.com/sonyprofessional/docs/cinealta_issue_7_issuu_r1/41 |author=Peter Crithary |editor=David Heuring |date=2016-02-08 |title=Interview with John Toll, ASC |magazine=CineAlta Magazine |issue=7 |page=41 |publisher=[[索尼|Sony]]|via=[[Issuu|Issuu]]|accessdate=2016-05-15}}</ref>和{{link-en|库克光学|Cooke Optics}}S4镜头完成大多数摄制。<ref name="sony">{{cite web |url=https://www.pro.sony.eu/pro/lang/en/eu/article/broadcast-products-netflix-sense8-nairobi-with-f55 |title=Christian Almesberger: making Sense8 in Nairobi with the F55 |work=[[索尼|Sony]]|accessdate=2016-05-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160515190804/https://www.pro.sony.eu/pro/lang/en/eu/article/broadcast-products-netflix-sense8-nairobi-with-f55 |archivedate=2016-05-15 |deadurl=no}}</ref>第1季摄制期间，曾在《云图》和《木星上行》中与沃卓斯基姐妹和格拉斯合作的托尔<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/awards/asc-career-honoree-john-toll-learned-from-best-1201703932/ |title=ASC Career Honoree John Toll Learned From the Best |author=David Heuring |date=2016-02-12 |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|accessdate=2016-05-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509184050/http://variety.com/2016/film/awards/asc-career-honoree-john-toll-learned-from-best-1201703932/ |archivedate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>亲自掌管芝加哥、<ref>{{Cite tweet |user=vicsoto |number=494582443316236289 |title=Slate for #Sense8 #chicago |date=2014-07-30 |author=Victor H. Soto |accessdate=2015-06-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508210040/https://twitter.com/vicsoto/status/494582443316236289 |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>旧金山、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rbthecraneguy.blogspot.com/2014/09/sense8-production-company.html |title=Sense8 |date=2014-09-19 |author=Robert Barcelona |work=rbthecraneguy.blogspot.com |accessdate=2015-06-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508210305/http://rbthecraneguy.blogspot.se/2014/09/sense8-production-company.html |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>伦敦、<ref>{{cite web |url=https://instagram.com/p/4R2q-ZQEGQ/ |title=Tuppence and Jamie, not amused. 🎬 #Sense8 #BTS |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |date=2015-06-23 |accessdate=2015-06-26 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824114818/https://www.instagram.com/p/4R2q-ZQEGQ/ |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>冰岛、<ref>{{cite interview |url=http://thefilmstage.com/features/john-toll-talks-adjusting-for-the-small-screen-sense8-the-wachowskis-more/ |title=John Toll Talks Adjusting for the Small Screen, 'Sense8,' the Wachowskis & More |work=The Film Stage |subject=John Toll |interviewer=Nick Newman |date=2015-11-24 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508221951/https://thefilmstage.com/features/john-toll-talks-adjusting-for-the-small-screen-sense8-the-wachowskis-more/ |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no }} [http://thefilmstage.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Sense-8-2-620x408.png Image] {{Wayback|url=http://thefilmstage.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Sense-8-2-620x408.png |date=20170825143736 }}</ref>和首尔的摄制工作。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://instagram.com/p/4XDVZ2QEOC/ |title=Lights, camera, 🌞. #Sense8 #BTS |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2015-06-26 |date=2015-06-25 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824114948/https://www.instagram.com/p/4XDVZ2QEOC/ |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>托尔摄像的方法是使用大量有些不必要的{{link-en|摄影机稳定器|Steadicam}}和{{link-en|手持摄像机|Hand-held camera}}来满足电视剧制作相对于他习惯的电影制作的更紧张的时间表。其余摄影师与其他导演一同在另外的地点工作，但他们都有同样的拍摄风格，因为他们也面临着同样的问题。<ref name="thefilmstage"/>麦克特格为墨西哥城<ref>{{cite web |url=https://instagram.com/p/4CQAAMQEEa/ |title=He's a lover, not a fighter. #Sense8 #BTS |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2015-06-26 |date=2015-06-17 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824115125/https://www.instagram.com/p/4CQAAMQEEa/ |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>和孟买<ref name="apdg"/>的摄制选择的摄影师是曾参与摄制他的作品[[神探愛倫坡：黑鴉兇殺案|神探愛倫坡：黑鴉兇殺案]]和[[倒數行動|倒數行動]]的丹尼·罗尔曼。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hdvideopro.com/technique/hd-dslr-filmmaking/outside-the-box-tools/ |title=Outside The Box Tools |work=HDVideoPro |date=2015-03-16 |author=Ian Blair |accessdate=2015-05-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508210926/http://www.hdvideopro.com/technique/hd-dslr-filmmaking/outside-the-box-tools/page-2 |archivedate=2016-05-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>提克威尔分别选择了{{link-en|弗兰克·格瑞比|Frank Griebe}}和克里斯蒂安·阿尔莫斯伯格一道完成柏林<ref>{{cite web |url=https://instagram.com/p/4NJ6AEQEHH/ |title=In the line of fire. #Sense8 #BTS |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2015-06-26 |date=2015-06-21 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160824115305/https://www.instagram.com/p/4NJ6AEQEHH/ |archivedate=2016-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>和内罗毕<ref name="sony"/>的场景。格瑞比曾参与包括《云图》在内的七部提克威尔作品的摄制，阿尔莫斯伯格则曾是《{{link-en|灵魂男孩|Soul Boy}}》和《内罗毕半条命》两部提克威尔作品的摄影师。

在第2季中，罗尔曼继续使用F55s，<ref name="F55S2"/>并在墨西哥城与麦克特格合作，<ref name="MexicoS2"/> 阿尔莫斯伯格与提克威尔一起在内罗毕工作，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BLzRxKvB5ho/ |title=Nairobi, the home of Van Damn! @tobyonwumere |date=2016-10-21 |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2016-12-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161231223458/https://www.instagram.com/p/BLzRxKvB5ho/ |archivedate=2016-12-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref>托尔则陪同拉娜·沃卓斯基负责其余地点的摄制。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BFERD-iwEPd/ |title=The #Road2Sense8 starts here. Welcome to Mumbai. |date=2016-05-06 |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2016-12-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161231223807/https://www.instagram.com/p/BFERD-iwEPd/ |archivedate=2016-12-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BEotxJ5wEEG/ |title=Country to country, coast to coast. Sensates are global. #BTS #Sense8 (📷: @anddicted) |date=2016-04-25 |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2016-12-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161231223607/https://www.instagram.com/p/BEotxJ5wEEG/ |archivedate=2016-12-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BIAQ2cIhV-I/ |title=Monday mornings with @freemaofficial. // #Road2Sense8 |date=2016-07-18 |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2016-12-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161231223935/https://www.instagram.com/p/BIAQ2cIhV-I/ |archivedate=2016-12-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="LA"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BJQs3McB_2N/ |title=Eréndira on her way to learn how to give a "close certo." #Road2Sense8 |date=2016-08-18 |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2016-12-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161231224030/https://www.instagram.com/p/BJQs3McB_2N/ |archivedate=2016-12-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BKBWhdGhxMu/ |title=When in Chicago... #Road2Sense8 |date=2016-09-06 |via=[[Instagram|Instagram]] |accessdate=2016-12-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20161231224141/ht