== 推广 ==
2015年7月开始，Netflix巴西分公司发布了一系列名为《超感8人组：解码》（{{lang-en|Sense8: Decoded}}）的纪录片。这些影片由胡奥·外尼尔（João Waine）执导，灵感来源于《超感8人组》，简要地涉及到了[[精神病学|精神病学]]、[[女性主義|女性主義]]、[[跨性別|跨性別]]和[[佛教|佛教]]等主题。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.otempo.com.br/divers%C3%A3o/lea-t-miguel-nicolelis-e-arthur-ver%C3%ADssimo-promovem-s%C3%A9rie-sense8-1.1073667 |title=Lea T, Miguel Nicolelis e Arthur Veríssimo promovem série 'Sense8' |date=2015-07-21 |work=otempo.com.br |accessdate=2016-10-31 |language=pt |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031220244/http://www.otempo.com.br/divers%C3%A3o/lea-t-miguel-nicolelis-e-arthur-ver%C3%ADssimo-promovem-s%C3%A9rie-sense8-1.1073667 |archivedate=2016-10-31 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.brasilpost.com.br/2015/07/28/netflix-feminista_n_7889720.html |title=Netflix lança mini-documentário feminista baseado na nova série 'Sense8' |date=2015-07-28 |work=[[赫芬顿邮报#国际版|HuffPost Brasil]]|author1=MdeMulher |author2=De Lucas Castilho |accessdate=2016-10-31 |language=pt |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031220405/http://www.brasilpost.com.br/2015/07/28/netflix-feminista_n_7889720.html |archivedate=2016-10-31 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://cargocollective.com/nandosperb/Sense8-Decoded-Netflix |title=Sense8 Decoded Netflix |work=cargocollective.com |accessdate=2016-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031220526/http://cargocollective.com/nandosperb/Sense8-Decoded-Netflix |archivedate=2016-10-31 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sense8decoded.com.br/ |title=Sense8: Decoded |work=sense8decoded.com.br |language=pt |accessdate=2016-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825095457/http://www.sense8decoded.com.br/ |archivedate=2015-08-25 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>同月稍晚时候，Netflix在[[Spotify|Spotify]]发布了一首名为《脑电波交响曲》（{{lang-en|Brainwave Symphony}}）的歌曲。<ref>{{cite AV media |url=https://play.spotify.com/track/40gtOsswUPQke4sSrNGvdb |title=Brainwave Symphony |via=[[Spotify|Spotify]] |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507201611/https://play.spotify.com/track/40gtOsswUPQke4sSrNGvdb |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>为了录制这首歌，他们记录下了八名路人在不同的刺激下各自的[[腦電圖|腦電圖]]，然后从这些脑电图中各截取出了一段旋律，并把它们按照该季的剧情走势安排顺序，混音得到了一首歌。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://businessinsider.com/netflix-symphony-combines-brainwaves-of-eight-strangers-2015-7 |title=Netflix composed a symphony by combining the brainwaves of eight strangers |author=Nathan McAlone |date=2015-07-31 |work=[[商业内幕|Business Insider]]|accessdate=2016-05-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507202021/http://businessinsider.com/netflix-symphony-combines-brainwaves-of-eight-strangers-2015-7 |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://sense8brainwavesymphony.com/ |title=We've made an original piece of music using peoples' brainwaves |work=sense8brainwavesymphony.com |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507202332/http://sense8brainwavesymphony.com/ |archivedate=2016-05-07 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>2015年8月上旬，Netflix上线了半小时时长的网络纪录片《超感8人组：创造世界》（{{lang-en|Sense8: Creating the World}}），在全世界拍摄来展示第1季的制作过程。<ref name="s8docu"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/10/arts/television/whats-on-tv-monday.html |title=What's On TV Monday |date=2015-08-10 |work=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2015-08-11 |author=Kathryn Shattuck |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150814090539/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/10/arts/television/whats-on-tv-monday.html |archivedate=2015-08-14 |deadurl=no}}</ref>

